<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>FoodBridge</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            background-color: #fefefe;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

            header img.logo {
                height: 40px;
            }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
            align-items: center;
        }

            nav a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #333;
                font-weight: 500;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

        .account-button {
            background-color: #f9c8b3;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            padding: 40px 60px;
            background: #fcf1ea;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .hero-text {
            max-width: 50%;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

            .hero-text h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
                font-weight: 800;
                color: #2f5130;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .hero-text p {
                font-size: 14px;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

            .hero-text button {
                margin-top: 20px;
                background-color: #2f5130;
                color: white;
                border: none;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border-radius: 10px;
                font-weight: bold;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

        .hero-images {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

            .hero-images img {
                width: 300px;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

        /* Soup Kitchen Section */
        .section {
            padding: 40px 60px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

            .section h2 {
                color: #2f5130;
                font-size: 22px;
                font-weight: 800;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }

            .section small {
                font-size: 12px;
                color: #777;
            }

        .soup-section {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 20px;
            gap: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

            .soup-section img {
                width: 250px;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .soup-section .text {
                max-width: 600px;
                font-size: 13px;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }

        .comment-box {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px;
        }

            .comment-box textarea {
                width: 100%;
                border: none;
                resize: none;
                font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
                font-size: 13px;
                outline: none;
            }

        .reactions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #555;
        }

        /* What We Do Section */
        .what-we-do {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

            .what-we-do h2 {
                color: #8b3c1f;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .what-we-do p {
                color: #444;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }

        .icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .icon-box {
            text-align: center;
        }

            .icon-box img {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .icon-box .label {
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #8b3c1f;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: url('footer-bg.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            padding: 30px 50px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 13px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

            .footer a {
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .footer .footer-logo {
                height: 40px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .footer .footer-left,
            .footer .footer-center,
            .footer .footer-right {
                flex: 1;
                min-width: 200px;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .footer .socials img {
                height: 20px;
                margin-right: 10px;
            }

        .donate-btn,
        .request-btn {
            background-color: #cf7958;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: block;
        }

        .policy-links {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <img src="logo-placeholder.png" alt="Logo" class="logo">
        <nav>
            <a href="#">ABOUT US</a>
            <a href="#">HOW IT WORKS</a>
            <a href="#">ABOUT FOOD WASTE</a>
            <button class="account-button">Account</button>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Bridging Communities Through<br>Food and Generosity</h1>
            <p>At FoodBridge, we connect local donors, vendors, and individuals with soup kitchens to reduce food waste and fight hunger. By redistributing surplus food, we ensure that nutritious meals reach those who need them most.<br><br>Join us in making a difference—one meal at a time.</p>
            <button>GET INVOLVED</button>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-images">
            <img src="kitchen1-placeholder.jpg" alt="Kitchen 1">
            <img src="kitchen2-placeholder.jpg" alt="Kitchen 2">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Find a Soup Kitchen to Help</h2>
        <small>Support local soup kitchens & charities by donation or volunteering.</small>
        <div class="soup-section">
            <img src="missionaries-placeholder.jpg" alt="Soup Kitchen">
            <div class="text">
                <p>
                    We are reaching out to kindly ask for your support in our ongoing donation drive to help those in need. Whether it's monetary donations, clothes, food, or other essentials, your contribution can make a big difference in the lives of individuals and families facing hardship. Every little bit counts, and with your help, we can bring hope and relief to our community. If you're willing to donate or would like more information, please don't hesitate to contact us. Thank you for your generosity and compassion.
                </p>
                <div class="comment-box">
                    <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Write a comment..."></textarea>
                    <div class="reactions">
                        👍 Like &nbsp; ❤️ Heart &nbsp; 😮 Wow &nbsp; 😢 Sad &nbsp; 😠 Angry
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="what-we-do">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>Our efforts in local communities create a ripple effect, connecting donors, vendors, and soup kitchens to reduce food waste and fight hunger.</p>
        <div class="icons">
            <div class="icon-box">
                <img src="connect-icon.png" alt="Connect Communities">
                <p class="label">Connect Communities</p>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-box">
                <img src="nourish-icon.png" alt="Nourish the Hungry">
                <p class="label">Nourish the hungry</p>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-box">
                <img src="sustainability-icon.png" alt="Promote Sustainability">
                <p class="label">Promote sustainability</p>
            </div>
            <div class="icon-box">
                <img src="inspire-icon.png" alt="Inspire Change">
                <p class="label">Inspire change</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-left">
            <img src="logo-footer.png" alt="Footer Logo" class="footer-logo">
            <p>© FoodBridge 2025</p>
            <p>900 San Marcelino St, Ermita, Manila, 1000 Metro Manila</p>
            <p>020 178 910 675</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:hello@foodbridgeemail.ph">hello@foodbridgeemail.ph</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-center">
            <a href="#">Food Waste Sources</a><br>
            <a href="#">Soup Kitchens in Manila</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-right">
            <div class="socials">
                <img src="fb-icon.png" alt="Facebook">
                <img src="ig-icon.png" alt="Instagram">
                <img src="tw-icon.png" alt="Twitter">
            </div>
            <button class="donate-btn">Donate Surplus Food</button>
            <button class="request-btn">Request Donations</button>
            <div class="policy-links">
                <a href="#">Cookies Policy</a> | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
